### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### ROUTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all routes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/routes

### Get route by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/routes/601

### Add new route
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/routes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Route_id": 604,
  "Distance": 410
}

