### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SERVICE HISTORY
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all service history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/servicehistory

### Get service history by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/servicehistory/701

### Add new service record
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/servicehistory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Record_id": 704,
  "Vehicle_id": 301,
  "Maintenance_Type": "Tyre Replacement",
  "Service_Date": "2024-03-10"
}

### Update service record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/servicehistory/704
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Vehicle_id": 301,
  "Maintenance_Type": "Tyre Replacement + Alignment",
  "Service_Date": "2024-03-10"
}

### Delete service record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/servicehistory/704

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### REPORTS — AGGREGATE FUNCTIONS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Total deliveries by each driver
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/deliveries-by-driver

### Route statistics (avg, max, min, total distance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/route-stats

### Vehicle count and capacity by availability status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/vehicle-status-summary

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### REPORTS — SET OPERATIONS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### UNION — combined driver and location contact list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/contact-list

### INTERSECT — vehicles in both Assignment and Service_History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/vehicles-in-both-tables

### EXCEPT — vehicles never assigned to any delivery
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/unassigned-vehicles

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### REPORTS — SUBQUERIES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Orders with delivery completed after 15:00
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/late-delivery-orders

### Driver assigned to earliest assignment
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/earliest-driver

### Vehicles with above average capacity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/above-avg-capacity

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### REPORTS — JOINS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### INNER JOIN — full assignment details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/assignment-details

### LEFT JOIN — all orders with delivery details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/orders-with-deliveries

### MULTI JOIN — full delivery report with duration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/full-delivery-report

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### REPORTS — VIEWS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Driver assignment summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/driver-assignment-summary

### Vehicle service report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/vehicle-service-report